						               													<description>Go through the ranks in making yourself the greatest stock market trader the world has ever seen! Investiture is modeled after various stock markets around the world, enabling you to understand how transactions work and all the while grow rich. It combines the intensity of the stock market with the strategy to become rich and have fun! This game requires no prior knowledge of how stock markets work! Be careful, because your decisions will affect every other player in the market!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On a turn a player may buy a stock, short a stock, or sell a stock they currently own. They may also play one of the lucky break cards in their hand. They get 3 turns per round and after each player has taken 3 turns, one at a time, all the cards are thrown in the middle to reflect the price changes of the stock.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is won when the players have decided to end the game. We typically suggest 10 rounds for full gameplay. The player who has the highest value in terms of cash in hand and stock market value on the board is declared the winner!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
